  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: d2a939c9b5142514086bd165cbbf93ed, type: 3}
  m_Name: MoreYes
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueObject
  dialogue:
  - Listen closely!
  - Long time ago this town was prosperous, rich and beautiful.
  - 'This town was blessed by Lunara, the god of the moon. '
  - 'And with her power this town was soon to be separate country. '
  - Maybe even counquer the world!
  - But the people of this town became greedy, unkind, and worst of all
  - They stopped worshipping their god.
  - Lunara became furious and cursed this town by eternal Crimson Moon.
  - Now eternal night is here full of nightmares.
  - All because these people couldn't value their god.
  - If it weren't for Lunara this town would be long forgotten.
  - But now... I'm surprised this town is still here after all those nightmares.
  - Ahh... I said enough! But since you were so kind to listen.
  - I will give you my ring. I think the broker said the value is around 100 coins.
  - Make good use of ti. For me its no longer valuable. Now be gone!
  responses:
  - responseText: Thanks!
    dialogueObject: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 5f6d9f37e672ed642b631288c810f5be, type: 2}
